metadata.name: Tranquility [宁静]
metadata.description:
Tranquility or [宁静], also means serenity. It is a state of being in which there is elegance in calmness and silence, and beauty in equanimity.

An attempt to craft a serene atmosphere that is soothing yet enchanting; a Xanadu in our chaotic world.

It is a piece that is about - peace.

2000 x 2000 pixels  
300 DPI
